@startuml lowtalkers_escape-reality

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor User

rectangle "Client (React)" {
  [App Component] as App
  [VR Scene Components] as VRScene
  [Authentication Components] as AuthComp
  [UI Components] as UIComp
}

rectangle "Server (Node.js/Express)" {
  [API Endpoints] as API
  [Controllers] as Controllers
  [Utilities] as Utils
}

database "MariaDB" as DB

cloud "AWS S3" as S3

User -> App : Interacts
App --> VRScene : Renders
App --> AuthComp : Manages auth
App --> UIComp : Renders UI

App --> API : HTTP Requests

API --> Controllers : Calls
Controllers --> DB : CRUD Operations
Controllers --> Utils : Uses

Utils --> S3 : Stores/Retrieves Images

@enduml